      "content": "i get that, but it feels so exhausting. the \"struggle\" you're talking about just feels like more pain. if the end result is always gonna be nothingness, isn't the struggle just making the inevitable harder? like, if they just embraced it, wouldnt it be more peaceful to just stop fighting and let the erasure happen? wouldn't it be easier to just... stop?",
